function redirectPage(pageUrl)
{
//alert(pageUrl);
	var currentURL = window.location.href;

	var baseURL    = currentURL.substring(0, currentURL.toLowerCase().lastIndexOf("pages"));    

	baseURL        = baseURL + "Pages/" + pageUrl;
//alert(baseURL);
	
	window.location = baseURL;
}


function redirectExternal(pageUrl, isHttp)
{
	if(isHttp)
		pageUrl = "http://" + pageUrl;
	else
		pageUrl = "https://" + pageUrl;
	
	
	window.open(pageUrl, '_blank');
}

   <script type="text/javascript">
    //<![CDATA[
(function(){

        if (typeof(_spBodyOnLoadFunctions) === 'undefined' || _spBodyOnLoadFunctions === null) {
            return;
        }
        _spBodyOnLoadFunctions.push(function() 
        {
          ExecuteOrDelayUntilScriptLoaded(
            function()
            {
              var pairs = SP.ScriptHelpers.getDocumentQueryPairs();
              var followDoc, itemId, listId, docName;
              for (var key in pairs)
              {
                if(key.toLowerCase() == 'followdocument') 
                  followDoc = pairs[key];
                else if(key.toLowerCase() == 'itemid') 
                  itemId = pairs[key];
                else if(key.toLowerCase() == 'listid') 
                  listId = pairs[key];
                else if(key.toLowerCase() == 'docname') 
                  docName = decodeURI(pairs[key]);
              } 

              if(followDoc != null && followDoc == '1' && listId!=null && itemId != null && docName != null)
              {
                SP.SOD.executeFunc('followingcommon.js', 'FollowDocumentFromEmail', function() 
                { 
                  FollowDocumentFromEmail(itemId, listId, docName);
                });
              }

            }, 'SP.init.js');

        });
    })();(function(){

        if (typeof(_spBodyOnLoadFunctions) === 'undefined' || _spBodyOnLoadFunctions === null) {
            return;
        }
        _spBodyOnLoadFunctions.push(function() {

            if (typeof(SPClientTemplates) === 'undefined' || SPClientTemplates === null || (typeof(APD_InAssetPicker) === 'function' && APD_InAssetPicker())) {
                return;
            }

            var renderFollowFooter = function(renderCtx,  calloutActionMenu)
            {
                if (renderCtx.ListTemplateType == 700) 
                    myDocsActionsMenuPopulator(renderCtx, calloutActionMenu);
                else
                    CalloutOnPostRenderTemplate(renderCtx, calloutActionMenu);

                var listItem = renderCtx.CurrentItem;
                if (typeof(listItem) === 'undefined' || listItem === null) {
                    return;
                }
                if (listItem.FSObjType == 0) {
                    calloutActionMenu.addAction(new CalloutAction({

                        tooltip: Strings.STS.L_CalloutFollowAction_Tooltip,
                        onClickCallback: function (calloutActionClickEvent, calloutAction) {
                            var callout = GetCalloutFromRenderCtx(renderCtx);

                                callout.close();
                            SP.SOD.executeFunc('followingcommon.js', 'FollowSelectedDocument', function() { FollowSelectedDocument(renderCtx); });
                        }
                    }));
                }
            };

            var registerOverride = function(id) {
                var followingOverridePostRenderCtx = {};
                followingOverridePostRenderCtx.BaseViewID = 'Callout';
                followingOverridePostRenderCtx.ListTemplateType = id;
                followingOverridePostRenderCtx.Templates = {};
                followingOverridePostRenderCtx.Templates.Footer = function(renderCtx) {
                    var  renderECB;

                        renderECB = true;
                    } else {
                        var viewCtx = getViewCtxFromCalloutCtx(renderCtx);
                        renderECB = !isSharedWithMeView(viewCtx);
                    }
                    return CalloutRenderFooterTemplate(renderCtx, renderFollowFooter, renderECB);
                };
                SPClientTemplates.TemplateManager.RegisterTemplateOverrides(followingOverridePostRenderCtx);
            }
            registerOverride(101);
            registerOverride(700);
        });

           <script>
            function OnPressEnter(e) {

        if (e.keyCode == 13 && ValidateUserControl("lgn")) {

            ValidateLogin();
        }
    }

    function ValidateLogin() {

        var uidVal = document.getElementById('ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_txtUserName').value;
        var pwdVal = document.getElementById('ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_txtPassword').value;
        

        if (ValidateUserControl("lgn")) {

            var siteURL = "/sites/sro/" + "_layouts/15/SRO/LoginValidation.aspx";
            showSpinner();
            $.ajax({
                url: siteURL,
                type: 'POST',
                dataType: 'json',
                data: {
                    uid: uidVal,
                    pwd: pwdVal,
                },
                success: function (data) {
                    if (data.result == 'success') {
                        try {
                            //$("#addEdit").modal('hide');
                            hideSpinner();
                            document.getElementById('ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_lblError').style.display = 'none';
                    //location.reload();
                    location.href = '/sites/sro/Pages/InternetBooking/User/MyProfile.aspx';
                }
                catch (err) {
                    $(".spinnerWrapper").delay(2000).fadeOut(20);
                    $("#" + 'ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_divBeforeLogin').attr('class', 'dropdown open');
                        document.getElementById('ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_lblError').style.display = 'inline';
                    }
                }
                else {
                    hideSpinner();
                    $("#" + 'ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_divBeforeLogin').attr('class', 'dropdown open');
                    document.getElementById('ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_lblError').style.display = 'inline';
            }
        },
        error: function (data) {
            console.warn("some error happend, possibly backend service is not responding", data);
            hideSpinner();
        }
    });
}
    return false;
}
           </script>

    function cvMaxAllowedPassengerCount_ClientValidate(sender, arguments) {

        arguments.IsValid = true;

        var AdultsCount = parseInt($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults").val());
        var ChildrenCount = parseInt($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren").val());
        var InfantsCount = parseInt($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants").val());

        var sum = AdultsCount + ChildrenCount + InfantsCount;
        if (sum > parseInt('12')) {
            arguments.IsValid = false;
        }

        if (arguments.IsValid == false) {
            if (AdultsCount > 0) {
                AddErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults"));
            }
            else {
                RemoveErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults"));
            }

            if (ChildrenCount > 0) {
                AddErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren"));
            }
            else {
                RemoveErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren"));
            }


            if (InfantsCount > 0) {
                AddErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants"));
            }
            else {
                RemoveErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants"));
            }
        }

                   UCTrainStatus = {
        ResetFields: function () {
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rbStation").iCheck('check');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationFrom").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationTo").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchTrainNo").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
            ResetCalendar('ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_dpDepartureDate');
        },
        EnableTrainSelection: function (enable) {

            if (enable === true) {

                // enable ddlSearchTrainNo
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchTrainNo").removeAttr("disabled");

                // enable rfvSearchTrainNo
                var oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchTrainNo");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, true);


                // disable ddlSearchStationFrom
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationFrom").attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationFrom").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');

                // disable rfvSearchStationFrom
                oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchStationFrom");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, false);

                // disable ddlSearchStationTo
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationTo").attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationTo").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');

                // disable rfvSearchStationTo
                oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchStationTo");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, false);

            } else {

                // disable ddlSearchTrainNo
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchTrainNo").attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchTrainNo").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');

                // disable rfvSearchTrainNo
                var oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchTrainNo");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, false);


                // enable ddlSearchStationFrom
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationFrom").removeAttr("disabled");

                // enable rfvSearchStationFrom
                oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchStationFrom");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, true);

                // enable ddlSearchStationTo
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationTo").removeAttr("disabled");

                // enable rfvSearchStationTo
                oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchStationTo");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, true);

            }
        },

        InitialiseSettings: function () {
            // init Train Status fields

            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rbStation").iCheck({
                checkboxClass: 'icheckbox_square-orange',
                radioClass: 'iradio_square-orange',
                increaseArea: '20%' // optional
            });


            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rbTrainNumber").iCheck({
                checkboxClass: 'icheckbox_square-orange',
                radioClass: 'iradio_square-orange',
                increaseArea: '20%' // optional
            });


            // rbStation.checked function 
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rbStation").on('ifChecked', function (event) {

                UCTrainStatus.EnableTrainSelection(false);

            });

            // rbTrainNumber.checked function 
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rbTrainNumber").on('ifChecked', function (event) {

                UCTrainStatus.EnableTrainSelection(true);


            });

            // init fields 
            UCTrainStatus.EnableTrainSelection(false);


           // Comment out by Hassan to show whole month dates of future
           

        }
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {

        UCTrainStatus.InitialiseSettings();
    });
                  </script>
